Domain Name Registration in India

It is very simple to access cheap domain name registration services with Vmaxinfo Institute. To get a particular name of domain, first you have to check its availability using online domain name availability checker tool on our website. It will examine and inform you about the availability of the domain name you are searching for.

This is important before you proceed with the registration process. If you find that the domain name is available then you just have to place an online order through our website. You are free to select from different types of options for payment like net banking, credit or debit cards, cheque/DD dispatch, cash cards, cheque or DD post to our office address.

Contact 0253-2582186, 7030314949 for domain registration.
